# PF6 Migration Context

## What Was Done

The Řehoř bot dashboard (`dashboard/`) was migrated from custom HTML/CSS to PatternFly 6 components.

## Components Converted

| Component | PF6 Components Used |
|-----------|-------------------|
| `App.tsx` header | Masthead, MastheadMain, Toolbar, ToolbarContent, ToolbarItem, ToolbarGroup |
| `App.tsx` nav | Nav (horizontal variant), NavList, NavItem |
| `App.tsx` instance selector | Select, MenuToggle, SelectList, SelectOption |
| `App.tsx` theme switcher | Dropdown, ToggleGroup, ToggleGroupItem, SunIcon, MoonIcon, AdjustIcon |
| `BotBanner.tsx` | Card (isCompact, isGlass), CardBody, Flex, Label, Icon, Button |
| `Instances.tsx` cards | Card (isCompact, isGlass), CardHeader, CardTitle, CardBody, CardFooter, Icon, CircleIcon, Label, LabelGroup, Content, Divider, Flex, FlexItem |
| `TaskCard.tsx` | Card (isCompact, isGlass), CardHeader, CardBody, Label, LabelGroup, Content, Flex |
| `MemoryCard.tsx` | Card (isCompact, isGlass), CardHeader, CardTitle, CardBody, CardFooter, Label, LabelGroup, Content |
| `DetailPanel.tsx` | Card (isGlass), CardHeader, CardTitle, CardBody, CardFooter, Button, Label, LabelGroup, DescriptionList, CodeBlock, Divider, TimesIcon |
| `CycleRunCard.tsx` | Card (isCompact, isGlass), CardHeader, CardTitle, CardBody, Label, LabelGroup, Button, Content, DownloadIcon |
| `CycleRuns.tsx` TaskGroupCard | Card (isCompact, isGlass), same pattern |
| `CycleRuns.tsx` CycleRunDetail | Card (isGlass), DescriptionList, Divider, Content, Button, ExpandIcon, CompressIcon, TimesIcon |
| `CycleRuns.tsx` TranscriptViewer | SearchInput, ToggleGroup, ToggleGroupItem, Button, Label, DownloadIcon |
| `Pagination.tsx` | PF Pagination (isCompact) |
| `Toasts.tsx` | AlertGroup (isToast), Alert, AlertActionCloseButton |
| `Tasks.tsx` filter | Select, MenuToggle, SelectList, SelectOption |
| `Memories.tsx` filters | Select (x3 for category, repo, tag) |
| `Search.tsx` | SearchInput |
| `Costs.tsx` | Card (isCompact, isGlass) for chart wrappers, ToggleGroup for metrics/date mode, Select for days |
| `ArchivedTasks.tsx` | Label, Content |

## Theme System

- Theme classes applied to `document.documentElement`: `pf-v6-theme-dark`, `pf-v6-theme-felt`, `pf-v6-theme-glass`, `pf-v6-theme-high-contrast`
- State persisted in localStorage keys: `pf-theme`, `pf-color-scheme`, `pf-contrast-mode`
- Custom CSS variables in App.css mapped to PF tokens with fallbacks
- Glass mode: Cards use `isGlass` prop; body uses `background-image` from PF token

## Still Using Custom CSS

- `.transcript-viewer` internals (message rendering, role colors)
- `.cycle-list` / `.cycle-row` table in Costs page
- `.split-layout` / `.split-main` / `.split-detail` page layout
- Recharts (data visualization — PF has no chart components)
- `EmbeddingMap.tsx` (canvas visualization)

## Mock Server

- Runs on port 8080 (`node dashboard/mock-server.mjs`)
- Vite proxies `/api` → `http://localhost:8080` and `/ws` → `ws://localhost:8080`
- Added 4 archived tasks (id 101-104) for testing Archive page
- Restart mock server after editing mock-server.mjs

